BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Pyw5BxikmyE9EJscOzkAa
SUMMARY:DUNE Mini-Comics Night
DTSTAMP:20260327T064717Z
DTSTART:20260328T130000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us today for the 100th edition of DUNE with an extra long 
	DUNE day! \\nOn Saturday\\\, March 28th participants will be creating comi
	cs and illustrations for the 100th issue of the mini-comic anthology DUNE.
	 Hugo House on Capitol Hill who partnered with the organizer Marc Palm in 
	2025 will host an eight hour long event celebrating this milestone. \\n \\
	nHugo House is large enough to accommodate 50-80+ participants normally\\\
	, more are expected for issue 100. Be prepared for some elbow to elbow spa
	ce. All are welcome despite skill level or experience. All artwork must be
	 started and finished within the time allowed in black & white and totally
	 analog. A special edition book will be published with all the submitted w
	ork and available to only contributors at the following month's meeting on
	 Tuesday April 28th. \\n \\nDune – Mini-Comics Night 100 will take place o
	n Saturday\\\, March 28th from 1pm – 9pm. Two drink minimum is required fr
	om the soda/beer/wine bar located in Hugo House. Bring your own materials 
	and ideas. Each participant will be asked to donate $10 – $20 (cash or dig
	ital payment) towards the cost of printing a special edition book. \\n \\n
	There will motivational tunes from a live DJ spinning records\\\, a limite
	d amount of snacks available\\\, as well as an "Inspiration Packet" given 
	out to the first 100 contributors.  \\n \\nContact the organizer/publisher
	 Marc Palm – \\nselfsatisfiedbooks@gmail.com or Hugo House welcome@hugohou
	se.org for \\nmore information. \\n \\nDUNE 100 Day \\n1-9 PM \\nHugo Hous
	e \\n1634 11th Ave\\\, Seattle\\\, WA 98122 \\n \\nPreregistering for this
	 event is highly recommend! Grab your free ticket below! \\n \\nFree admis
	sion to this event is made possible with support from 4Culture.\n\nhttps:/
	/hugohouse.org/event/_2026-03-28/\n\nFrom Hugo House
URL:https://hugohouse.org/event/_2026-03-28/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:hugo-house
CATEGORIES:Hugo House
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT8H
END:VEVENT
